The missiles that are availible only work if you first lock on to the
target. You do this by simple using the pointer on the normal view screen
and clicking on your target.

The missiles work only if your target doesnt have an ECM (they have a 100km
range).
The smart missiles overide normal ECM systems but not the naval versions
and has a greater explosive power.
The nave grade missiles explode BIG TIME and are immune to any known ECM
system.


